<p class="ql-align-center">正面有拍摄键和功能键两个实体按键</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201201/bfbb5682fad7489a9b76f93e14baa4fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侧面是电源按键</p>
